873, 227.8866, 228.7583, 226.7137, 226.1773, 226.0861, 225.2613, 225.9813, 226.703, 226.0581, 226.1161, 226.3967, 226.7322, 226.3381, 226.3, 226.9821, 227.0424, 226.1794, 226.8329, 227.1913, 226.6276, 226.7785, 227.0274, 227.3859, 226.9608, 227.0989, 227.1074, 227.5073, 228.1852, 228.2435, 228.4152, 228.5073, 228.0605, 228.4026, 227.8007, 227.6598, 228.0547, 228.261, 228.026, 227.7707, 228.3935, 228.2923, 227.7996, 226.9986, 227.3415, 227.0798, 226.6964, 225.8675, 226.6575, 226.2123, 225.7347, 226.9989, 228.1832, 228.5505, 229.5014, 229.6527, 228.0819, 229.0344, 230.5437, 229.9961, 230.2647, 229.8414, 227.544, 226.5358, 227.524, 228.4762, 227.3659, 226.8375, 227.5466, 227.5841, 227.0258, 228.8414, 229.2015, 228.3839, 227.3974, 227.8754, 228.3547, 229.9759, 229.7006, 228.4612, 228.3038, 228.4056, 229.6999, 229.4691, 229.8723, 231.3033, 230.7382, 231.9097, 230.3184, 231.3438, 233.2615, 233.9238, 235.7299, 236.3924, 234.2596, 233.3395, 232.1452, 234.005, 233.6815, 231.9582, 233.0019, 232.581, 234.2741, 233.7104, 235.2741, 236.2834, 236.5088, 237.2033, 238.3131, 239.4998, 239.2414, 238.1028, 236.8247, 239.3512, 239.4613, 242.537, 242.2141, 243.9326, 246.0178, 246.6291, 246.2472, 244.0513, 243.2169, 241.69, 239.64, 238.7482, 238.6571, 236.5216, 236.1596, 236.6456, 235.2813, 237.2074, 236.3576, 237.1691, 237.0675, 232.7474, 231.987, 233.3199, 233.3742, 230.7032, 231.251, 228.1264, 228.5309, 231.4105, 231.5232, 231.3514, 230.612, 230.177, 224.103, 224.2696, 225.7559, 224.6102, 223.6637, 226.2341, 227.7994, 226.6663, 226.1968, 228.4742, 227.4941, 225.9267, 225.3015, 224.4897, 224.8306, 224.3764, 222.24, 222.2671, 223.5472, 222.4421, 221.0576, 223.6295, 222.4985, 221.5167, 218.1165, 215.9536, 218.4809, 215.1368, 214.7834, 215.8816, 214.9757, 215.8775, 213.6385, 216.6489, 216.6656, 217.6863, 216.3555], "summary_html": "<h1>商品期货alpha因子拾遗 -- 通过 (Sharpe 1.36)</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本报告提取了4个商品期货截面alpha因子：时序回归因子、复合动量因子、仓单因子和基差动量因子。核心思路是利用截面排名做多空组合（top 20%多、bottom 20%空）。其中时序回归因子通过OLS回归同时捕捉趋势强度和流畅性，仓单因子利用仓单数据的年同比变化反映供需格局变动。最终复现中，时序回归因子与仓单因子的等权组合（经时序标准化）取得了最佳的风险调整收益。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.98</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>4.7%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.8%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-10.1%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.05</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.07</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>-0.45</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.4 / 0.82</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.58</td><td>1.95</td><td>1.76</td><td>0.13</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.14</span></td><td>0.81</td><td>0.8</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.76</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.95</span></td><td>0.92</td><td>0.84</td><td>0.76</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.06</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-3.5</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ry</code></td><td>展期收益</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>receipt</code></td><td>仓单</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每日</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>63</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>89.4%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>39.7</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<h3>因子1：时序回归因子</h3>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{close}_t = a + b \\cdot t + c \\cdot t^2, \\quad t = 1, 2, \\ldots, J</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Factor} = b \\times R^2</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">b</span> 为一次项回归系数（趋势强度），<span class=\"math-tex\">R^2</span> 为回归拟合优度（趋势流畅性），<span class=\"math-tex\">J</span> 为回看窗口。</p>\n<h3>因子2：复合动量因子</h3>\n<p>先按 <span class=\"math-tex\">J</span> 日收益率 <span class=\"math-tex\">r_{t-J,t}^i</span> 的正负将品种分为正收益组和负收益组，再在各组内按截面排序：做多正收益组中排名最高的品种，做空负收益组中排名最低的品种。</p>\n<h3>因子3：仓单因子</h3>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">wrt_t = \\frac{\\frac{1}{J}\\sum_{i=t-J+1}^{t} C_i}{\\frac{1}{126}\\sum_{k=t-306}^{t-180} C_k}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">C_i</span> 为第 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span> 天的标准仓单数量。分母为一年前同期（上下各约一季度）的平均仓单数量。仓单同比增长越大做空，反之做多（BMT）。</p>\n<h3>因子4：基差动量因子</h3>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">BM_t = \\text{Carry}_t - \\text{Carry}_{t-J} = ry_t - ry_{t-J}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">ry</span> 为展期收益率（roll yield），反映期限结构斜率的同比变化。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>所有gate通过，Sharpe 1.27。换手率0.74较高。时序IC=0.005（弱）</td><td>实现全部4因子共16变体</td><td>tsreg_J243_K10_raw Sharpe 1.27</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>IC gate可提升，换手率可降低</td><td>加入IC gate过滤弱品种、增加长持有期变体(K=15,21)、增加tsreg+warehouse组合变体</td><td>combo_tsreg_wh_ts Sharpe 1.36，新增57变体含cs/ts标准化</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>尝试降低vol_target至0.12减少换手冲击</td><td>全面降低vol_target、扩大combo参数网格</td><td>Sharpe 1.34（略低于R2），pipeline自动保留R2 spec_best</td></tr></table></div>\n<p>关键转折点：R2引入时序回归+仓单组合变体是关键提升，两个低相关因子（一个量价类、一个基本面类）的组合效果显著优于单因子。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种商品期货（72个品种参与回测）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 10-21日持有期效果最佳</li>\n<li><strong>核心数据字段</strong>: close（量价）、receipt（仓单/基本面）、ry（展期收益）</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 时序回归因子计算较慢（per-symbol Python loop做OLS），在大品种集上约需10-20秒\n<p>- 仓单数据非空率约29%，部分品种缺失 - 2021年动量崩溃期间因子回撤明显（2021年Sharpe为负） - <code>_ts</code> 标准化变体Sharpe虽高但杠杆极高，实盘需控制总敞口</p>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9466</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 8.25s</li>\n</ul>"}